*******************************************************************             
*                                                                 *             
*    SWAPPARM - ORVYL Swap System I/O request parameters           *            
*                                                                 *             
*******************************************************************             
         SPACE                                                                  
*                                                                               
* Prefix for every request                                                      
*                                                                               
#SWAPCOM RECORD BEGIN                                                           
#SWAPCMD DS    A                                                                
*                                                                               
* Swap Device I/O command codes                                                 
*                                                                               
#SWCOPEN EQU   4                       Open action code                         
#SWCCLOS EQU   8                       Close I/O code                           
#SWCREAD EQU   12                      Read I/O code                            
#SWCWRIT EQU   16                      Write I/O code                           
#SWCRSET EQU   20                      Reset I/O code                           
         END   ,                                                                
         SPACE 2                                                                
*                                                                               
* Swap Device Open request                                                      
*                                                                               
#SWPOPEN RECORD BEGIN                                                           
#SWPOCMD DS    XL(L'#SWAPCOM)                                                   
#SWPALLO DS    A                       Data set allocation info                 
#SWPINFO DS    A                       Data set info return area                
         END   ,                                                                
         SPACE 2                                                                
*                                                                               
* Swap Device Close request                                                     
*                                                                               
#SWPCLOS RECORD BEGIN                                                           
#SWPCCMD DS    XL(L'#SWAPCOM)                                                   
         END   ,                                                                
         SPACE 2                                                                
*                                                                               
* Swap Device Read/Write request                                                
*                                                                               
#SWPDO   RECORD BEGIN                                                           
#SWPDCMD DS    XL(L'#SWAPCOM)                                                   
#SWPBLK  DS    A                       Starting block number                    
#SWPLIST DS    A                       Pointer to page list                     
#SWPCNT  DS    H                       Total number of pages                    
         END   ,                                                                
         SPACE 2                                                                
*                                                                               
* Swap Device Reset request                                                     
*                                                                               
#SWPRSET RECORD BEGIN                                                           
#SWPRCMD DS    XL(L'#SWAPCOM)                                                   
         END   ,                                                                
